08-Sniffing

    Perform active sniffing
        Perform MAC flooding using macof
            macof -i eth0 -n 10 and press Enter.
                -i: specifies the interface and -n: specifies the number of packets to be sent (here, 10
        Perform a DHCP starvation attack using Yersinia
            yersinia -I(Starts an interactive ncurses session.)
            F2 to select DHCP mode
            x to list available attack options.
            The Attack Panel window appears; press 1 to start a DHCP starvation attack.
        Perform ARP poisoning using arpspoof
            arpspoof -i eth0 -t 10.10.10.1 10.10.10.1
                -i: specifies network interface and -t: specifies target IP address.
        Perform an Man-in-the-Middle (MITM) attack using Cain & Abel
            using to get PASSWRODS with arppoisoning, really nice
        Spoof a MAC address using TMAC and SMAC
            using a tool to change macs

    Perform network sniffing using various sniffing tools
        Perform password sniffing using Wireshark
            sniffing de red por wireshark
            filtros para buscar contraseñas
            http.request.method == POST
        Analyze a network using the Omnipeek Network Protocol Analyzer
            free trial
            analizador de red.stats ,etc
        Analyze a network using the SteelCentral Packet Analyzer
            free trial
            analizador de red.stats ,etc
            Arp, protocolos, ports, reportes, etc

    Detect network sniffing
        Detect ARP poisoning in a switch-based network
            Utilizando wireshark para encontrar duplicados
        Detect ARP attacks using XArp
            detecta automaticamente, muy facil
        Detect promiscuous mode using Nmap and NetScanTools Pro
            nmap --script sniffer-detect(Modo promiscuo detectará) resultado:1111111111111
            Netscantoools Pro, detecta en una opcion ¨manual tools-> promiscous scanner¨
